                p Opt for Shouft's auto-links or input your choices for a personalized link.

        div(class="col-lg-3 col-md-5 col-sm-8 row justify-content-center mb-5")
            div(class="mb-2 d-flex justify-content-center h-50")
                img(
                  style="width: 150px;height: 150px;"
                  src="../static/img/security-icon.png" class="icon"
                )
            div(class="row h-auto align-items-start text-center icon-text")
                h2 Security
                p Press SHORT to encrypt your URL, rendering it inaccessible to anyone but you.
                    
        div(class="col-lg-3 col-md-5 col-sm-8 row justify-content-center mb-5")
            div(class="mb-2 d-flex justify-content-center h-50")
                img(
                  style="width: 150px;height: 150px;"
                  src="../static/img/speed-icon.png" class="icon"
                )
            div(class="row h-auto align-items-start text-center icon-text")
                h2 Efficiency
                p Elevate productivity with highly optimized web services for time-saving solutions.
                    
